Invocation Name: unreached people
des:
Unreached People is a skill that provides prayer guidance for the unreached people group of the day, compliments of the Joshua Project, a ministry of FRONTIER VENTURES.

To get started, just say "Alexa, launch Unreached People" or "Alexa, open Unreached People".

At anytime, you can stop by saying "Alexa, stop"
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
